{"tid":2512010,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"晉環買家搶記者電話","createTime":"2021-05-01T10:51:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T11:40:10.000Z","uid":39464,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"223a6887c472cce9594228d791f059683c4a7d11","tid":2512010,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T10:51:22.000Z","msg":"路勁黃竹坑站上蓋晉環開售，吸引大批買家前往認購。記者通常都會現場採訪賣樓情況，並訪問買家覺得所購買的樓盤質素如何，或者相關資金多少，如果買家不想接受訪問，其實亦可以拒絕。不過今次本報記者就遇到一名買家搶去記者電話後，再用記者的電話反拍攝記者。<br />\n<br />\n消息指該名女子是晉環的買家，並與其男伴購買了兩伙單位，記者見到買家後，上前禮貌詢問其男伴：「先生，請問可否講兩句？」，該名女子上前並問：「是否想影相？」記者禮貌回應「沒錯」，但不料該名女子突然搶去記者電話，用記者電話拍攝記者並說：「是否這樣（拍照）？」<br />\n<br />\n隨後記者取回電話，該名女子便一言不發急步離開。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210501/O63VI7Y4IVGFPLWQ5ZB4ATXAVE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210501%2FO63VI7Y4IVGFPLWQ5ZB4ATXAVE%2F&d=Z1ElB6oaYTZYlgUQOIdQNnpsBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=8b96d431\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210501%2FO63VI7Y4IVGFPLWQ5ZB4ATXAVE%2F&h=ee166bce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210501/O63VI7Y4IVGFPLWQ5ZB4ATXAVE/</a>"},{"pid":"3442120351a4ad67895ba584855da996fe74f43a","tid":2512010,"uid":45830,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T10:52:04.000Z","msg":"成件事，好戇鳩"},{"pid":"67ac1f925d53d50a82c15d72f5f434da332edc5c","tid":2512010,"uid":259010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"223a6887c472cce9594228d791f059683c4a7d11","tid":2512010,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T10:51:22.000Z","msg":"路勁黃竹坑站上蓋晉環開售，吸引大批買家前往認購。記者通常都會現場採訪賣樓情況，並訪問買家覺得所購買的樓盤質素如何，或者相關資金多少，如果買家不想接受訪問，其實亦可以拒絕。不過今次本報記者就遇到一名買家搶去記者電話後，再用記者的電話反拍攝記者。<br />\n<br />\n消息指該名女子是晉環的買家，並與其男伴購買了兩伙單位，記者見到買家後，上前禮貌詢問其男伴：「先生，請問可否講兩句？」，該名女子上前並問：「是否想影相？」記者禮貌回應「沒錯」，但不料該名女子突然搶去記者電話，用記者電話拍攝記者並說：「是否這樣（拍照）？」<br />\n<br />\n隨後記者取回電話，該名女子便一言不發急步離開。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210501/O63VI7Y4IVGFPLWQ5ZB4ATXAVE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210501%2FO63VI7Y4IVGFPLWQ5ZB4ATXAVE%2F&d=Z1ElB6oaYTZYlgUQOIdQNnpsBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=8b96d431\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210501%2FO63VI7Y4IVGFPLWQ5ZB4ATXAVE%2F&h=ee166bce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210501/O63VI7Y4IVGFPLWQ5ZB4ATXAVE/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T10:52:09.000Z","msg":"香港人不嬲有錢大晒架啦"},{"pid":"ad9542dcfc4479104a5c672fed547450947f0702","tid":2512010,"uid":204539,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T10:53:10.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"orange\">有無買家想同白卡做鄰居</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d8ddf682eb048c5de1b676894f7f4dbe47b87e0","tid":2512010,"uid":222809,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T10:57:59.000Z","msg":"暴露自己係白卡人士<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97bd2e9dadd61bf57b027c76a758329437a984f9","tid":2512010,"uid":40812,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T11:00:21.000Z","msg":"我覺得條女嬲又唔怪得晒佢喎<br />\n<br />\n問咗人介唔介意講二句先影，會好過你影住問人介唔介意講二句嘅"},{"pid":"9c0835d0b88c289b86d03c812cbbdf529346594e","tid":2512010,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T11:01:22.000Z","msg":"睇個樣似公務員。"},{"pid":"85e3a98fce89e513c4de1bfb6d57d689de9f44fe","tid":2512010,"uid":150842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"97bd2e9dadd61bf57b027c76a758329437a984f9","tid":2512010,"uid":40812,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T11:00:21.000Z","msg":"我覺得條女嬲又唔怪得晒佢喎<br />\n<br />\n問咗人介唔介意講二句先影，會好過你影住問人介唔介意講二句嘅"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T11:02:29.000Z","msg":"咪係<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=